ðŸ”¹ Problem Statement (Rewritten Simply)

You are given an array of integers.

You must:

Start from index 0

Add only elements at EVEN indices (0, 2, 4, â€¦)

Keep adding one by one

STOP immediately when the sum becomes greater than 50

