4	40
ðŸ”¹ STEP-BY-STEP WALKTHROUGH
ðŸŸ¢ Start
sum = 0

ðŸ”¹ Index 0 (even) â†’ ADD
sum = 0 + 10 = 10

ðŸ”¹ Index 1 (odd) â†’ SKIP
sum = 10

ðŸ”¹ Index 2 (even) â†’ ADD
sum = 10 + 5 = 15

ðŸ”¹ Index 3 (odd) â†’ SKIP
sum = 15

ðŸ”¹ Index 4 (even) â†’ ADD
